      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FROLICNEARTHESEA NZ (5) hasn't raced since April last year but showed plenty of talent in a brief maiden campaign, winning on debut at Melton before a Listed placing at the same venue. Has switched to the Bain yard since and was readied with a nice trial. Well placed for a winning return. ZANY GIRL (6) is racing well, scoring at Globe Derby two runs ago before boxing on for third at her latest appearance. Suited returning to circuit where she has recorded two wins and placing in three appearances. NITEONTHETOWN (1) owns a 50 per cent strike rate at this circuit and distance, coming from this barrier to win the last time he raced here three back. ELLA KATE (3) cannot be left out after a string of top-four results, the latest a sound second at Globe Derby.",
